Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.50,0:00:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#26 回归忧国之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.87,0:00:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空袭又开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.64,0:00:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人拦截到船员的通讯吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.38,0:00:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.48,0:00:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全没有可以窃听的电波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.58,0:00:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.75,0:00:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在立刻收集电脑空间内的可使用区域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.32,0:00:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,确保能够传送300万人记忆和Ghost的空间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.12,0:00:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎？这么突然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.29,0:00:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没时间了，动作快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.13,0:00:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.00,0:01:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种事情，能办到吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.57,0:01:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.87,0:01:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我找不到其它可以拯救难民的方法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.00,0:01:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.97,0:01:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了...了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.98,0:01:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我刚刚叫支援AI在电脑空间确保可使用的区域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.51,0:01:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备完毕之后，就开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.78,0:01:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢相助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.19,0:01:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,借由将Ghost整个传送到网络上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.72,0:01:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假设我们可以活下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.49,0:01:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那没有电子脑化的人怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.56,0:01:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对亲友当中有这类人的人来说\N应该很难接受这个结论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.50,0:01:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们大概会对我感到失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.87,0:01:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自行离开出岛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.01,0:01:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这种状况之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.77,0:01:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,指导者的任务常常既重大又充满不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.21,0:01:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站在不得不指引多数人的立场上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.82,0:01:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有时会因情况被迫做出独断的决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.99,0:01:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些，他们应该也会了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.62,0:02:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果真是这样，就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.16,0:02:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.36,0:02:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我到少校那边的最短路线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.50,0:02:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.73,0:02:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是往大桥去了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.77,0:02:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去找少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.57,0:02:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.81,0:02:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通讯断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.95,0:02:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核导弹会不会趁空袭后的混乱发射呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.75,0:02:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从潜艇几乎没有通讯的状况来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.96,0:02:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发射时间或许早就决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.66,0:02:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.49,0:02:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从宙斯盾舰的距离以及微机械散布的时机来观察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.96,0:02:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,AM 10:00 这个时间很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.20,0:02:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，你们实际上是怎么想的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.24,0:02:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把难民的记忆上传到网络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.88,0:02:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的能够维持Ghost存在吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.32,0:03:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,记忆虽然是生命活动很重要的要素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.52,0:03:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，没有Ghost就只是单纯的数据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.56,0:03:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，少校不是把一线\N希望寄托在这上面吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.66,0:03:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这我也知道，可是这实在\N是很乱来的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.73,0:03:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是这么想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.43,0:03:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是继续做下去，也没办法\N救巴特先生他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.70,0:03:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，我觉得应该不\N要理会少校的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.41,0:03:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 咦？你在说什么啊！\N- 不懂你的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.44,0:03:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,- 那该怎么办？\N- 我做不到啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.98,0:03:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.68,0:03:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全不回应我的呼叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.45,0:03:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,热线明明是通的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就表示……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.41,0:03:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.46,0:03:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不甘心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.09,0:03:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我确实是国会解散重新改选时打选战的广告牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.13,0:03:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，我从未被如此刻薄的对待过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.41,0:03:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高仓既然做到这个地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.64,0:03:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要用我的方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.64,0:04:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收拾这个局势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.61,0:04:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您要跟哪里联系呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.82,0:04:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.69,0:04:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是第8个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.76,0:04:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种运算，我可是高手中的高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.83,0:04:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再搞定一个，就肯定能在\N导弹轨道上布下弹幕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.87,0:04:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然照你说的，违反少校的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.90,0:04:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，进行卫星坠落作业\N真的是正确的选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.04,0:04:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.34,0:04:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.44,0:04:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明进行得很顺利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.91,0:04:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.91,0:04:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这说不定是搭载我们AI的卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎？……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.49,0:04:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么，为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.52,0:04:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是美帝的卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.85,0:04:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.56,0:04:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们看来好像是借用了\N从日本发射的美帝卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.40,0:04:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.40,0:04:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果安保条约缔不缔结\N还不是得听那些家伙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.80,0:05:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校为什么要把我们的AI放在那种地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.01,0:05:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许是想反过来\N对美帝搞谍报之类的工作吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.01,0:05:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然搞不清楚那么多\N但这下可伤脑筋了……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.75,0:05:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经没有时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.36,0:05:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石川先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.66,0:05:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.90,0:05:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我必须跟大家一起去某个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.27,0:05:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.27,0:05:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.88,0:05:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.14,0:05:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.28,0:05:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校他们的事情就拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.58,0:05:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.55,0:05:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.69,0:05:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下来就真的是一个人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.30,0:05:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.17,0:06:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.21,0:06:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你会折纸鹤吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.01,0:06:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,纸鹤？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.18,0:06:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.35,0:06:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且只用一只左手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.28,0:06:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要使用控制软体\N任何人都会折的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.55,0:06:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.43,0:06:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你会折吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.19,0:06:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只用左手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.83,0:06:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.96,0:06:36.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(75,228)}{\fad(300,400)}I do
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.16,0:06:36.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(75,240)}{\fad(300,400)}作词：Ilaria
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.36,0:06:36.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(75,252)}{\fad(300,400)}作曲：菅野洋子(Yoko kanno)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.56,0:06:36.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(75,264)}{\fad(300,400)}演唱：Ilaria graziano
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.44,0:06:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也是依靠孤独生活下去的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.57,0:06:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名字呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.64,0:06:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之前一直没问，叫什么名字呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.34,0:06:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假名倒是有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.31,0:06:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这点你也是一样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.31,0:06:55.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Nell' illusione ho creduto alla mia forza inesorabile\N在梦幻中，我相信自己无畏的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.81,0:06:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.05,0:06:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难民帮我取了好几个名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.44,0:07:01.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,e inevitabilmente sono diventata debole\N却软弱到无法逃避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.92,0:06:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我虽然是为了拯救他们\N才和他们一起行动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.52,0:07:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但也许只是为了填补孤独
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.04,0:07:06.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ora sento gli eventi si transformano e so già\N我现在所能感知的，是那变换的时空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.64,0:07:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才跟他们在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.00,0:07:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是到最后还是没能填补
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.14,0:07:16.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,di emozioni che aprono ricordi lontani\N强烈的感情唤起久远的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.14,0:07:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为即使被人依赖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.43,0:07:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己却无法依赖别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.04,0:07:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有可以交心的对象吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.84,0:07:23.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,nell'anima ritrovo la speranza che nel corpo stanco ormai\N灵魂重新感受希望，而精疲力竭的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.31,0:07:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不能说是没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.52,0:07:29.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ha smesso di vibrare come un fuoco spento dal mio pianto\N却如同泪水浇熄的火焰般停止跳跃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.71,0:07:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.08,0:07:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直……都在寻找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.54,0:07:35.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,tra le mani un filo d'acqua porterò con me e\N用双手汲取，哪怕是一掬水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.13,0:07:42.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,nel deserto un filo d'erba sopravviverà\N沙漠里就会有些许的草生存下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.03,0:07:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.86,0:07:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,导弹不会飞到大桥附近来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.74,0:07:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要慌，快点过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.34,0:07:47.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I do,I do
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.83,0:07:52.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,gridare contro gli occhi spenti e gelidi\N我对着他寒冷似冰的眼睛哭喊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.19,0:07:58.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,per essere sempre di più\N总有一天会比现在更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.54,0:08:02.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I do,I do
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.28,0:08:06.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,oltrepassare mondi inespugnabili\N超越磐石般的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.75,0:08:12.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,senza temere nulla più...\N为了不再畏惧虚无
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.03,0:08:16.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I do,I do
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.21,0:08:21.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,emeregere dal fondo per lottare e poi\N挣扎着想从沉沦中飞升起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.41,0:08:27.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,salire in alto più che mai\N升至前所未有的高度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.65,0:08:31.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I do,I do
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.51,0:08:35.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,guardare nel futuro e sorridere\N望着未来而微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.04,0:08:41.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,con una nuova identità\N与全新的自我一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.59,0:08:52.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,fino a quando il sole sorgerà...\N待到太阳升起之时……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.00,0:08:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,素子！！
