Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.01,0:09:24.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(75,240)}{\fad(300,400)}作词:やなせたかし
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.11,0:09:23.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(75,252)}{\fad(300,400)}作曲:いずみたく
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.41,0:09:23.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(75,264)}{\fad(300,400)}原唱:岛谷瞳(Hitomi Shimatani)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.24,0:09:28.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ぼくらはみんな 生きている\N我们大家都活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.11,0:09:32.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生きているから 悲しいんだ\N因为活着才会悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.48,0:09:40.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手のひらを太陽に 透かしてみれば\N让阳光透过你的手掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.08,0:09:47.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,まっかに流れる 僕の血潮\N我的热血鲜红地流淌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.46,0:09:51.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,みみずだって おけらだって\N不管是蚯蚓还是蝼蛄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.83,0:09:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会有这种事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.83,0:09:53.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,あめんぼだって\N或者是水蝇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.70,0:09:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们大家一定\N是有Ghost的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.70,0:09:59.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,みんなみんな 生きているんだ\N我们大家都活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.40,0:10:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了，普路托？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.40,0:10:02.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,友達なんだ\N都是好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.81,0:10:07.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ぼくらはみんな 生きている\N我们大家都活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.75,0:10:11.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生きているから わらうんだ\N因为活着才会欢笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.78,0:10:15.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ぼくらはみんな 生きている\N我们大家都活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.78,0:10:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上传：全体塔奇克马的记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.69,0:10:19.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生きているから うれしいんだ\N因为活着才会快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.99,0:10:27.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手のひらを太陽に 透かしてみれば\N让阳光透过你的手掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.63,0:10:34.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,まっかに流れる 僕の血潮\N我的热血鲜红地流淌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.97,0:10:39.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,とんぼだって かえるだって\N不管是蜻蜓还是青蛙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.58,0:10:43.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,みつばちだって\N或者是蜜蜂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.88,0:10:48.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,みんなみんな 生きているんだ 友だち...\N我们大家都活着，都是好朋友……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.09,0:10:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么回事，普路托？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.39,0:10:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.16,0:10:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看样子，塔奇克马跟卫星\N一起去撞核弹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.00,0:11:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克马？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.70,0:11:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阻止了最糟糕的事态发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.77,0:11:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.20,0:11:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的情况，我不太了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.47,0:11:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎因为部下的牺牲\N阻止了核导弹的发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.35,0:11:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,部下的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.75,0:11:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先不说这个，刚刚您提到的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.95,0:11:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.32,0:11:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,导弹毁了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.36,0:11:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正茅葺的行动将\N促使冷战构造完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.67,0:11:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，这样一来他就当不上英雄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个爆炸是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.58,0:11:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.58,0:11:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到了塔奇克马的歌声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.28,0:11:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些小鬼帮我们挡下来了么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.57,0:12:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.67,0:12:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.97,0:12:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,AI采取了跟我的命令不同的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.04,0:12:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，你没事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.88,0:12:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克马它们……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.82,0:12:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,课长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.79,0:12:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果总理联系的地方……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.83,0:12:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.33,0:12:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，现在必须先抓住\N官房长官与合田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.57,0:12:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这件事也有可能在我们\N有生之年都不能公开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.07,0:12:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先迅速进行，事后处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.74,0:12:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.21,0:12:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.48,0:13:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,官房长官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.12,0:13:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您应该知道我们到这里来的理由吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.89,0:13:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是政变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.56,0:13:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是以战争为借口的屠杀行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.86,0:13:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我无法眼睁睁看着他们用核弹自爆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.06,0:13:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本就没有这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.37,0:13:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,写下这个剧本的应该是您\N还有内厅的合田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.70,0:13:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合田？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.41,0:13:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是在考虑国家未来的前提下\N提前缔结新安保条约而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.24,0:13:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是一场跟难民之间的战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.85,0:13:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,长官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.12,0:13:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下来，您将在非公开状态下\N接受严格查问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.22,0:13:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早就有心理准备了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说起来……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.59,0:13:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你比我预料的更像个女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.96,0:13:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我不知道你感情用事\N跑去向哪边求助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.30,0:13:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但这个国家不依靠美帝\N是无法存活下去的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.30,0:13:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您恐怕有什么误会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.27,0:13:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎核弹没有爆炸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.44,0:14:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.78,0:14:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要发射第二枚吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.71,0:14:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.68,0:14:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,确认从东北方南下的飞机\N属于哪一方再说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.39,0:14:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是机身上如果\N有八一徽标的话……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.36,0:14:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一身独立，而至一国独立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.36,0:14:20.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出自福泽谕吉《劝学》，日本当代政治名言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.60,0:14:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自始至终，就是这样思考和行动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.14,0:14:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茅葺政权将一如既往\N在同美帝、美俄联盟、中国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.64,0:14:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及亚洲、E.U(欧盟)各国\N保持同等政治距离之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.91,0:14:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,依照独自的判断行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.98,0:14:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,摸索在联合国的协调路线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.40,0:14:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,航空自卫军的秘密部队么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.90,0:15:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经确认到日本方面的意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.34,0:15:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请带他走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.34,0:15:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.25,0:15:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总理命令我们来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.98,0:15:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请快点上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.39,0:15:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.89,0:15:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.92,0:15:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这把刀，请物归原主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.64,0:15:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斋藤、帕兹、博玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.51,0:15:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，你没事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.30,0:15:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.51,0:15:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思，要麻烦你们\N向自卫军汇报详细情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.31,0:15:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.80,0:15:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.51,0:16:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是公安9课的石川？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.65,0:16:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你把那个交给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.05,0:16:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.42,0:16:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.12,0:16:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要小看人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.89,0:16:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们9课可是最擅长打架和情报战的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.03,0:16:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奴隶之国要是怠于侍奉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.64,0:16:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消费之国必然会致饥饿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.44,0:16:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人手不足虽然让劳动制造业获利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.74,0:16:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是过度主张权力\N资本主义的血脉将会硬化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.51,0:16:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我国虽然彻头彻尾自称是资本主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.38,0:16:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实际却是理想化的社会主义国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.99,0:17:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是累积了废物\N就需要能够操作血液分离的大脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.06,0:17:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一点对歌颂自由平等的贵国来说\N应该也是一样的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.83,0:17:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.10,0:17:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是真心话和场面话还得区别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.54,0:17:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.71,0:17:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.88,0:17:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必这么急着去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.55,0:17:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,荒卷先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.79,0:17:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.46,0:17:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合田一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.03,0:17:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你涉嫌犯有预备或阴谋内乱罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.43,0:17:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及预备或阴谋触犯\N私自对外国发动战争罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.73,0:17:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你跟我们走一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.30,0:17:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,官房长官大致已经承认所涉罪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.21,0:17:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而你最后的导演也宣告失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.78,0:17:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，现在逮捕我已经没有意义了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.15,0:17:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.92,0:18:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我与官房长官之间无论\N何时都是Stand Alone的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.55,0:18:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更何况我亲手写的报告书\N现在应该已经送到警察厅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.29,0:18:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们不知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.83,0:18:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于这种犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.90,0:18:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刑法上规定只要自首\N其罪行就一概不问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.64,0:18:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去需要我才能的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.44,0:18:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的要这样做吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.95,0:18:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里有总理的手谕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.82,0:18:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总理对你的能力给予了很高评价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.09,0:18:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，当这种能力有可能\N流失到国外的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.02,0:18:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总理要求我们全力阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.49,0:18:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根据情况甚至不惜射杀目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.30,0:18:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打算怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.87,0:18:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必在意，只是口头威胁罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.00,0:18:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.37,0:18:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦？是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.51,0:19:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就去死吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.42,0:19:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.56,0:19:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是……！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.99,0:19:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们这些家伙！从什么时候\N开始介入这件事的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.13,0:19:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,课长！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.30,0:19:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快，不能让他被灭口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.04,0:19:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.75,0:19:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.66,0:19:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,纸鹤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.36,0:19:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,纸鹤？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.13,0:19:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话说回来，这个微机械还真有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.53,0:19:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以死得毫无痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.97,0:19:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然你是个让人感兴趣的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.70,0:20:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，对我们而言你是危险因素
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.74,0:20:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贵国不需要\N有领导魅力却无法控制的领袖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.91,0:20:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有顺从的消费者就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.68,0:20:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我……先走……了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.27,0:20:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.60,0:20:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在哪里偷懒呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.71,0:20:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到新浜4区跟阿兹玛与普路托会合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.74,0:20:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.98,0:20:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要求的追加预算都通过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.85,0:20:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻壳车，确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.85,0:20:47.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ウチコマ：漫画Ghost in the Shell中的攻壳车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.95,0:20:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yes，Sir
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.22,0:20:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.09,0:20:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次事件，造成了很多牺牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.43,0:21:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难民问题退回到了原点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.40,0:21:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茅葺总理主张的独立、共同竞争路线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.37,0:21:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对于国民来说也是荆棘之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.84,0:21:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从今往后\N会越来越需要我们这样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.38,0:21:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.34,0:21:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.68,0:21:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么一副事不关己的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.25,0:21:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校，你该不会已经看破红尘了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.09,0:21:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.12,0:21:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到第329期国家审议会\N已经通过预算的报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.53,0:21:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.83,0:21:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中止樱花的24小时监视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.70,0:21:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从现在开始返回工作岗位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.90,0:21:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总算……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.13,0:21:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.74,0:21:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经快无聊死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.34,0:21:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是事先开着暖气就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.37,0:21:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校就是要这样才对嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.91,0:21:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,简报怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.54,0:21:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用脑潜入来做吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.25,0:21:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，你先去负责指挥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.02,0:21:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我等一下过去会合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.95,0:21:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.69,0:22:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.43,0:22:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不……没事
